    "Remove the engine\n See operation\n\"Engine, Remove and Install\".",
    "Attach the engine to the assembly stand KM-412 .\n 2 technicians\nrequired\n \n\n\n\n•  \nDetach the retaining cables from the engine lifting eyes.",
